history.text: Hi. Our movie is Iron Man
Hi! It is Iron Man! How do you feel about the movie?
I have never honestly seen it, but based on the ratings I would say it is pretty good.
I have seen it, and I do enjoy Robert Downey Jr.
Do you typically enjoy superhero films?
Are you a fan of superhero films, like this movie?
LOL!! Yes, I do enjoy watching them with my little ones.
LOL we think alike. I typically prefer comedies.
I didn't realize tha this movie was he first film made for Marvel
I also was not aware that Gwyneth Paltrow was in the movie
Yes, she was in the movie! It isn't a typical movie you would see her in though
Did you find the ending predictable or surprising?
I found it predictable. Most of the time, the movies are very predictable to me
Do you enjoy the way that special effects are being brought on screen, such as in this movie, with flying and jumping and such
I agree.
I do enjoy how far the movies have developed in special effects
What was your favorite part
I think my favorite part was when he put the exoskeleton on for the first time
I know you haven't seen it, was this something you would ever watch?
Possibly! I keep my options open with what I watch.
I have seen a few super hero movies to have a general idea of the story line of this one
Agreed. I do the same. I think the rating on this is pretty accurate.
From reading the key scenes, the movie seems pretty intense
Yes, I agree that there are many scenes that have you at the edge of your seat!
He seems to enjoy disclosing his identity
What do you think of the critical response on this movie?  If you were to read it before seeing the movie, would you watch it?
I think it sounds very energetic, aside from the review saying that it is slightly depressed
I do not understand where the slightly depressing is, I need to rewatch it to see what they saw
I think they are referring to the plot being similar to other superhero movies
I can see that, I believe Marvel has a plot that seems similar in all their comics, as well as on screen.
It looks as though we can finish the conversation! It was great talking to you!
I find it interesting that they call this movie a "military thriller"
You too!
I saw that too!

uid2response.feedback: It was very hard to figure out what to talk about in the movie. I had not seen it in a long time, but the other person had not seen it at all.
